i Khuy\u1ebfn kh\u00edch: S\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m Vaseline Radiant Cream SPF30 PA++  tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 312,000 VND\n\n\ud83d\udccc Ti\u00eau ch\u00ed \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1:\n\nHi\u1ec7u \u1ee9ng lan t\u1ecfa (40%): D\u1ef1a tr\u00ean t\u1ed5ng l\u01b0\u1ee3t xem, l\u01b0\u1ee3t th\u00edch v\u00e0 l\u01b0\u1ee3t chia s\u1ebb tr\u00ean TikTok\nCh\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u1ed9i dung (60%): Ban Gi\u00e1m Kh\u1ea3o \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 d\u1ef1a tr\u00ean s\u1ef1 s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o, t\u00ednh th\u1ea9m m\u1ef9 v\u00e0 th\u00f4ng \u0111i\u1ec7p l\u00e0m \u0111\u1eb9p khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Vaseline Radiant Cream\n\n\ud83c\udf1f \u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t: Ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh c\u00e1c nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 trong chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u1eadn th\u00eam qu\u00e0 t\u1ea1i link H5 c\u1ee7a ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh: https://activity.tiktok.com/t/ZSSuXCD4y/\n\n\u2728 Lan t\u1ecfa c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng ch\u0103m da r\u1ea1ng r\u1ee1 \u2013 tham gia #GocLamDep ngay h\u00f4m nay!", "profileLarger": "https://p19-common-sign.tiktokcdn-us.com/tiktok-obj/9a50db9c7c9d7ec7f23c905af7f940fa.jpeg~tplv-tiktokx-origin.image?dr=9627&x-expires=1770094800&x-signature=jHHx%2FdlXWv2OBn1UAzbUGEDAKcw%3D&t=4d5b0474&ps=13740610&shp=81f88b70&shcp=9b759fb9&idc=useast5", "profileMedium": "https://p19-common-sign.tiktokcdn-us.com/tiktok-obj/9a50db9c7c9d7ec7f23c905af7f940fa.jpeg~tplv-tiktokx-origin.image?dr=9627&x-expires=1770094800&x-signature=jHHx%2FdlXWv2OBn1UAzbUGEDAKcw%3D&t=4d5b0474&ps=13740610&shp=81f88b70&shcp=9b759fb9&idc=useast5", "profileThumb": "https://p19-common-sign.tiktokcdn-us.com/tiktok-obj/9a50db9c7c9d7ec7f23c905af7f940fa.jpeg~tplv-tiktokx-origin.image?dr=9627&x-expires=1770094800&x-signature=jHHx%2FdlXWv2OBn1UAzbUGEDAKcw%3D&t=4d5b0474&ps=13740610&shp=81f88b70&shcp=9b759fb9&idc=useast5", "coverLarger": "", "coverMedium": "", "coverThumb": ""}, {"id": "7367694564414455824", "title": "huyennguyenwinmi", "desc": "", "profileLarger": "", "profileMedium": "", "profileThumb": "", "cover